$ %VSINSTALLDIR%Common7\Redist\MSVC\x.y.z

In (at least some → Windows/development/Visual-Studio/versions[versions]) of a → Windows/development/Visual-Studio[Visual Studio/VC] installation, this directory contains the installer
files for the *Visual C++ Redistributable Files*: `vcredist_x64.exe`, `vcredist_x86.exe`, `vc_redist_x64.exe` and `vc_redist.x86.exe`.

sa:
  The registry key `→ Windows/registry/tree/HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE/Software/Microsoft/VisualStudio/14_0/VC/Runtimes`
